{"type": "article", "id": 21160, "title": "干洗店回收的衣架，你有想过可以这样用吗？", "description": "给人提供了一种不同的视角。", "date": "2016-01-25T07:00:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 22568, "name": "City of Dreams Pavilion"}, {"id": 22569, "name": "设计竞赛"}, {"id": 22570, "name": "Folio"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607101556HGSlfRVvbO1MJFAE.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>City of Dreams Pavilion 是由纽约一些建筑委员会举办的比赛，<a href=\"http://newyork.figmentproject.org/2016pavilion\" target=\"_blank\">旨在促进可持续发展的思想。</a>要求参赛者使用回收材料设计凉亭（ Pavilion），每年 8 月份申请提交，第二年 1 月份公布名单。获胜者将在曼哈顿以南的 Governors Island（总督岛）展示长达半年。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>今年胜出的 Hanger Barn 来自纽约建筑事务所 Folio ，他们使用了从干洗店回收的衣架，搭建成两个拱形的“棚”。</span>白色的衣架通过特别的方式叠在一起，像是立起来的花纹，有种特别的<span>轻盈感，也有点像地上吹起来的气泡。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>从不同的角度看花纹的疏密关系不同，在阳光的照射下它的阴影也有了层次。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101550QHKIEkOoPneDSq3z.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101550bTIP5g1CWnY7FaUm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>中间有一个缺口，让两个空间相连。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101551Oy4oB8e3pKrAl9HJ.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101551HhP98YWnVG1ID2m5.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.41880342\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101552I9lgdqehHWOwNu2A.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.4284188\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>Governors Island（总督岛）曾经是美国重要的军事基地，整个 20 世纪，都由国家海岸防卫队（U.S Coast Guard）驻扎。直到 2003 年，纽约州政府接管后，将它改建成了公园和教育基地并对公众开放。游客可以从曼哈顿南端经水路登岛参观，</span><span>City of Dreams Pavilion 的</span><span>装置都将展示到夏天，成为岛上观光游览的一部分</span><span>。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2010 年是第一届，来自 </span>BEHIN HA DESIGN STUDIO 。凉亭是用牛奶箱搭建的，以木材做结构，每一个箱子的底部铺上了一层土壤，种上绿色植物。植物朝内生长，但阳光和雨水依然可以透过土壤促进光合作用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101552grLWXsRlYB86A4Tc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101553DrA5Jh7pNMVSECtZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2015 年的获胜作品更重视发挥材料本身的特征，分别使用了尼龙绳和废弃的伞。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101554FGBqP5H9QRoxg0Nm.jpg\" title=\"The Billion Oyster Pavilion by BanG Studio \" alt=\"The Billion Oyster Pavilion by BanG Studio \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101554A7sYV2d81zDjblhT.jpg\" title=\"The Billion Oyster Pavilion by BanG Studio\" alt=\"The Billion Oyster Pavilion by BanG Studio\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>The Billion Oyster Pavilion by BanG Studio</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101555hkA3iPBmctxZefID.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101555uNsWDXcKeGTfU5CF.jpg\" title=\"Organic Growth by Izaskun Chinchilla Architect\" alt=\"Organic Growth by Izaskun Chinchilla Architect\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Organic Growth by Izaskun Chinchilla Architect</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/01/19/folio-hanger-barn-installation-new-york-governors-island-city-of-dreams-pavilion-competition-dezeen/\" target=\"_blank\">dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://newyork.figmentproject.org/2016pavilion\" target=\"_blank\">figmentproject</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}